page.title: 10Ecology
page.content: When we went up Mill Lane we found 13 different kinds of tree,1 conigerous and 12 deciduous. We kept on walking and identified 28 spring flowering plants, 11 summer flowering,7 Autumn flowering. There are many different plants living along the River Windrush which flows through the block and a completely different set of plants living around the dry stone walls in the area. Mnay wild animals also live in the area including rats, fieldmice, woodmice, harvestmice, rabbits, hares,foxes,badgers,stoats,deer,wild cats to name just a few. We have very little pollution in the area as we have no factories and little traffic passing through.
